# 9T-vs-6T-SRAM-Reliability-Analysis
# Nanoscale CMOS Memory Design and Reliability Analysis

## Overview

This project presents the design, simulation, and reliability analysis of conventional 6T SRAM and advanced 9T SRAM architectures using 45nm CMOS technology in Cadence Virtuoso.

The objective was to improve SRAM stability, reduce leakage power, enhance soft-error tolerance, and increase reliability for nanoscale VLSI applications.

