- Designed 6T SRAM and 9T SRAM architectures
- Cadence Virtuoso based simulation
- 45nm CMOS Technology
- Read, Write and Hold Operation Analysis
- Static Noise Margin (SNM) Analysis
- Leakage Power Analysis
