## SRAM Architectures

### Conventional 6T SRAM

- Smaller Area
- Faster Implementation
- High Read Disturbance
- Lower Noise Margin
- More Vulnerable to Soft Errors

### Proposed 9T SRAM

- Higher Stability
- Better Static Noise Margin
- Reduced Leakage Power
- Improved Reliability
- Better Radiation Tolerance

