## Results

| Parameter | 6T SRAM | 9T SRAM |
|------------|------------|------------|
| Stability | Moderate | High |
| Read Disturbance | High | Very Low |
| Leakage Power | Higher | Lower |
| Soft Error Tolerance | Poor | High |
| Reliability | Lower | Higher |

